    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;docs-internal-guid-73154fa8-7fff-cf17-f511-893e62f174d3&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;fter his exile to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;Dapitan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;, in Zamboanga del Norte in 1892, José Rizal found himself in a remote, quiet corner of the Philippines—far from the political unrest and revolutionary fervor he had helped fuel. Despite being forcibly removed from Manila and his active involvement in the reform movement, Rizal’s exile didn’t stop him from continuing his work as an intellectual and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;community leader&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;. He embraced his new role as a community builder, contributing to Dapitan in various capacities: as a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;physician&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;teacher&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;scientist&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;, and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;farmer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
